  <h2>rhymer</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="https://landesbergn.github.io/rhymer/"><code>rhymer</code></a>
    is an R package to find rhyming words. It's a wrapper around the
    <a href="https://www.datamuse.com/api">Datamuse API</a> and is published on
    <a href="https://cran.r-project.org/package=rhymer">CRAN</a>.
  </p>
