    A 'database' of various NYC bar &amp; restaurant closings since COVID-19
    radically changed the restaurant landscape.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/landesbergn/nyc_restaurants">Code</a> — includes scraping scripts</li>
